snippet.title: Amberlynn Reid says NO MORE trolling & KEEPS TROLLING.
snippet.description:
READ: I meant nephew, not niece! She filmed beckys nephew.*

i literally think this is one of my best ALR videos yet and i cant wait for yalls comments ily

show and episode i used 'its me or the dog' (incredible show btw lol): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MfqZwbNXOJ0&t=389s&ab_channel=It%27sMeortheDog

also u know how this idea came to my head? lmao u prob dont care but ill tell u- someone on FB was dealing with an aggressive dog exactly like this onem where the dog doesnt respect her, i remembered this episode and referenced her to it, then i clicked it myself to kinda watch it for fun and when i heard the name BECKY LMAOOOO my head started RUNNING i was laughing so much just imagining the edited version lolll, the bit i used is so perfect too, bc it mirrors how amber disrespects becky and even after they broke up she still keeps mentioning her and trying to put herself above her any way she can thats all LOL if u read it ily
